_sText:
Simple prefab on how to speed up or slow down mid-map without server-side plug-ins. tutorial on how to make this:
deleted due to change of acc on youtube.

to have speed ups/slow downs on various parts of the map, simple parent a trigger_multiple to the highspeed_trigger

to adjust speed gain/loss edit the parameter override. < 1 = speed loss, > 1 = speed gain

you can delete the banners (as u can probably not even see them properly) they were just for my tutorial, no function to them.
